; pnpm config for the build-only bundle deps. minimum-release-age is in
; MINUTES; 14400 = 10 days. Supply-chain guard: never install a version
; published less than 10 days ago, giving a compromised release time to be
; caught before it can enter a build. Bumping a dep means it must be >= 10
; days old. Kept in .npmrc, not pnpm-workspace.yaml: this is a single package,
; not a pnpm workspace.
minimum-release-age=14400
